quran[11{c,v,t}:
21,91,aur woh khatoon jis ne apni asmat ki hifazat ki thi hum ne uss ke andar apni rooh se phonka aur ussay aur uss ke betay ko duniya bhar ke liye nishani bana diya
21,92,"yeh tumhari ammt haqeeqat mein aik hi ammt hai aur mein tumhara rab hon, pas tum meri ibadat karo"
21,93,magar ( yeh logon ki karstani hai ke ) unhon ne aapas mein deen ko tukre tukre kar dala sab ko hamari taraf palatna hai
21,94,"phir jo naik amal kere ga, iss haal mein ke woh momin ho, to is ke kaam ki na qadri nah ho gi, aur ussay hum likh rahay hain"
21,95,aur mumkin nahi hai ke jis bastii ko hum ne halaak kar diya ho woh phir palat sakay
21,96,yahan taq ke jab Yajooj o majooj khol diye jayen ge aur har bulandi se woh nikal parrin ge
21,97,"aur wada barhaq ke poora honay ka waqt qareeb aa lagey ga to yaka yak unn logon ke daiday phatay ke phatay reh jayen ge jinhon ne kufar kya tha kahin ge"" haae hamari kam bakhti, hum iss cheez ki taraf se ghaflat mein parre hue thay, balkay hum khata car thay """
21,98,"be shak tum aur tumahray woh mabood jinhein tum pujte ho, Jahannum ka eendhan hain, wahein tum ko jana hai"
21,99,"agar yeh waqai khuda hotay to wahan nah jatay ab sab ko hamesha isi mein rehna hai """
21,100,wahan woh phunkaraymarain ge aur haal yeh ho ga ke is mein kaan pari aawaz nah sunai day gi
21,101,"rahay woh log jin ke liye hamari taraf se Bhlai ka pehlay hi faisla ho chuka hoga, to woh yaqeenan uss se door rakhay jayen ge"
